      <BlogCrossLinks title="Scrabble Words Starting With Q" />
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Scrabble Words Starting With Q — QUIZZIFY, QUARTZ, QUIRKY & QUINTET</h1>
      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400"><time datetime="2026-06-29">June 29, 2026</time><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><span>5 min read</span><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔍</span> Solver</a> <a href="/activities/#quiz" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🎯</span> Quiz</a> <a href="/activities/#anagram" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔀</span> Anagram</a> <a href="/activities/#rack" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🎲</span> Rack</a> <a href="/activities/#wotd" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">📖</span> WOTD</a> <a href="/sixty-seconds/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">⏱️</span> 60s</a></div>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Q is worth 10 points — the joint-highest tile value in Scrabble. But it's also the most feared tile because most Q words require U. Master Q-starting words and you'll turn that feared tile into a scoring machine. QUIZZIFY alone delivers 40 points without even hitting a premium square.</p>
      <div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-950/30 to-yellow-950/20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500/70">👑 Top Scorer</div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">QUIZZIFY</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-300 font-semibold mb-3">40 points — Q(10) + U(1) + I(1) + Z(10) + Z(10) + I(1) + F(4) + Y(4)</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">An 8-letter bingo candidate scoring 90 points with the bonus. Requires Q, both Z tiles, plus common letters — legendary when achievable.</p>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top Q-Starting Words</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏆 QUIZZIFY — 40 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Q + both Z tiles + F + Y. The ultimate Q-word. Bingo = 90 total.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">💎 QUARTZ — 24 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Q(10)+U(1)+A(1)+R(1)+T(1)+Z(10). Deploys Q and Z together. Classic.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🤪 QUIRKY — 22 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Q(10)+U(1)+I(1)+R(1)+K(5)+Y(4). K and Y add extra punch after Q.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🎶 QUINTET — 16 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Q(10)+U(1)+I(1)+N(1)+T(1)+E(1)+T(1). All common tiles around Q.</p></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Q Without U — Emergency Plays</h2>
      <p>When you draw Q without U, these words save you from being stuck with a -10 penalty at game end.</p>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">QI</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">11 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">QOPH</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">18 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">QADI</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">14 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">QANAT</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">14 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">QWERTY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">21 pts</span></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Q-Word Strategy</h2>
